::Prowl::

Setting Iron Raptor down near the Ark, Prowl comes to a very abrupt stop 
against one of the ship's sides, his wing snapping at the impact.

He transforms to his robot mode and walks over to Iron Raptor.

"Are you allright?" he asks, concern in his voice.
